How do I get set up?
Dependencies:
npm install
npm install jsonwebtoken
npm install -g mocha
How do I run smoke test?
Update bootstrap.js to have smoke test point at your expected endpoint:
test\sutaxi\bootstrap.js
Example:
global.endpointMikeqa = "https://0d8aksreg6.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/qa17";
Smoke test takes around 6 minutes:
mocha test/sutaxi/api/smoketest/*
Trip full-flow smoke test takes around 3 minutes:
mocha test/sutaxi/api/smoketest/1.setup-drivers.js
mocha test/sutaxi/api/smoketest/4.trips.js
